highlights.text: CORTIS has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “FaSHioN” is the highest at #3.
“No Broke Boys” by Disco Lines and Tinashe has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 103 days straight.
“AMOR BANDIDO” by J. Eskine, Oruam, and Alef Donk is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 34 spots at #65.
“Titik Nadir (feat. Monita Tahalea)” by Kahitna and Monita Tahalea is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #94.
